\f111\fs16\insrsid207967\charrsid15561226 won the PEN/ Faulkner Award. Other novels include }{\i\f111\fs16\insrsid207967\charrsid15561226 Americana }{\f111\fs16\insrsid207967\charrsid15561226 (1971), }{\i\f111\fs16\insrsid207967\charrsid15561226 End Zone 
