he night's combined sounds came washing in with a freshness and renewed immediacy. For the first time in minutes we looked at each other, knowing the new sound was an amplified voice but not sure what it was saying. Heinrich returned, walking}{
\f111\fs16\insrsid2510831\charrsid15561226  }{\f111\fs16\insrsid10622856\charrsid15561226 in an over-deliberate and stylized manner, with elements of stealth. This seemed to mean he was frozen with significance.
