\par I went upstairs and told Denise not to worry. I would take a}{\f111\fs16\insrsid2510831\charrsid15561226  }{\f111\fs16\insrsid10622856\charrsid15561226 
tablet from the bottle and have it analyzed by someone in the chemistry department at the college. I waited for her
 to tell me she'd already done that. But she just nodded grimly and I headed down the hall, stopping in Heinrich's room to say goodnight. He was doing chinning exercises in the closet, using a bar clamped to the doorway.
\par "Where did you get that?"
\par "It's Mercator's."
\par "Who's that?"
\par "He's this senior I hang around with now. He's almost nineteen and he's still in high school. To give you some idea."
\par "Some idea of what?"
\par "How big he is. He bench-presses these awesome amounts."
\par "Why do you want to chin? What does chinning accomplish?" What does anything accomplish? Maybe I just want to build up my body to compensate for other things."
\par "What other things?"
\par "My hairline's getting worse, to name just one."
\par "It's not getting worse. Ask Baba if you don't believe me. She has a sharp eye for things like that."
\par "My mother told me to see a dermatologist."
\par "I don't think that's necessary at this stage."
\par "I already went."
\par "What did he say?"
\par "It was a she. My mother told me to go to a woman."
\par "What did she say?"
\par "She said I have a dense donor site."
\par "What does that mean?"
\par "She can take hair from other parts of my head and surgically implant it where it's needed. Not that it makes any difference. I'd. just as soon be bald. I can easily see myself totally bald. Ther
e are kids my age with cancer. Their hair falls out from chemotherapy. Why should I be different?"
\par He was standing in the closet peering out at me. I decided to change the subject.
\par "If you really think chinning helps, why don't you stand outside}{\f111\fs16\insrsid2510831\charrsid15561226  }{\f111\fs16\insrsid10622856\charrsid15561226 the closet and do your exercises facing in? Why stand in that dark musty space?"
\par "If you think this is strange, you ought to see what Mercator's doing."
