\par "Every time I see newsfilm of someone in his fourth week of sitting in a cage full of snakes, I find myself wishing he'd get bitten."
\par "So do I," Heinrich said.
\par "Why is that?"
\par "He's asking for it."
\par "That's right. Most of us spend our lives avoiding danger. Who do these people think they are?"
\par "They ask for it. Let them get it."
