put him at ease, get him to talk about himself, about Dylar. Part and parcel of my plan. My plan was this. Swivel my head to look into rooms, put him at his ease, wait for an unguarded moment, blast him in the gut three times for maximum efficiency of pai
n, take his Dylar, get off at the river road, shut the garage door, walk home in the rain and the fog.
