ctures man erects for safety. Furthermore this novel is itself a tightly looped fiction and is a closing of a large loop in DeLillo's career: he returns not only to America, but also to some of the circumstances and methods of }{
\i\f111\fs16\insrsid10622856\charrsid15561226 Americana }{\f111\fs16\insrsid10622856\charrsid15561226 and }{\i\f111\fs16\insrsid10622856\charrsid15561226 End Zone. }{\f111\fs16\insrsid10622856\charrsid15561226 Becau
