ins by "spraying [Jack] with German"\emdash a language which Jack, despite his Sisyphean attempts to learn it, cannot understand. However, it is better that he can't, for from the nun bursts}{\f111\fs16\insrsid2510831\charrsid15561226  }{
\f111\fs16\insrsid10622856\charrsid15561226 A storm of words. She grew more animated as the speech went on. A gleeful
